title: Seattle's Suzzallo performs "River" & more Live on KEXP

author: KEXP
description:
http://KEXP.ORG presents Suzzallo performing live in the KEXP studio. Recorded May 29, 2025.

The Destroyer 03:23
River 07:04
Constellations 15:59
Star String Radio 21:58 

Rocky Votolato - Guitar, Vocals
Stephen Bonnell - Bass Guitar
Rudy Gajadhar - Drums

Host: John Richards
Audio Engineer: Kevin Suggs
Mastering Engineer: Julian Martlew

Cameras: Jim Beckmann, Carlos Cruz, Scott Holpainen & Luke Knecht
Editor: Luke Knecht
